Put libhackgmc.so in your home folder :)

Copy and past the fallowing lines in terminal if you want to enable creative hacks

cd ~
sudo mv libhackgmc.so /opt/minecraft-pi-reborn-client/mods

Copy and past the fallowing lines in terminal if you want to dissalbe creative hacks

cd /opt/minecraft-pi-reborn-client/mods
sudo mv libhackgmc.so ~